-- ===========================================================================
-- World generation + customization for the CAVES shard (underground world).
-- 世界生成与定制 — 洞穴分片（地下世界）。
--
-- Same format as the Master shard's leveldataoverride.lua (see that file's
-- header for the full explanation). The differences here are cave-specific:
-- location is "cave", roads are disabled, and the overrides table lists cave
-- creatures and resources (worms, slurtles, mushrooms, nightmare creatures,
-- toadstool, etc.).
-- 格式与主世界分片的 leveldataoverride.lua 相同（详见该文件头部说明）。
-- 区别在于洞穴特有配置：location 为 "cave"，道路已禁用，
-- 覆盖表列出洞穴生物及资源（蠕虫、蜗牛龟、蘑菇、噩梦生物、蟾蜍王等）。
--
-- Easiest way to regenerate: customize the caves on the in-game "Host Game"
-- screen, host once, then copy the generated file from the save directory.
-- 推荐生成方式：在游戏内 "Host Game" 界面定制洞穴，开服一次，
-- 然后从存档目录中复制生成的文件。
--
-- Keep required_prefabs = { "multiplayer_portal" } so players can travel
-- between the surface and caves.
-- 务必保留 required_prefabs = { "multiplayer_portal" } 以确保地表与洞穴间互通。
-- ===========================================================================
return {
  background_node_range={ 0, 1 },
  desc="Delve into the caves... together!",
